                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18370814-name-385" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18370814-name-385" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18370814-name-385" type="surname" value="ARGENT"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18370814-name-385" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>JOHN ARGENT</persName>
                  </hi>. I am in the employ of Mrs. Sarah Low, a blacking maker. On the 27th of July I came home with the cart with this money in a bag—I left the cart a few minutes, and then missed the bag and money—the prisoner was in her employ—I did not authorise him to take any money that day.</p>
